            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>white long grain rice </strong>to the casserole dish with your <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong>, <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong>, <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong>, <strong>soy sauce </strong>and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span><strong> boiled water</strong>, give everything a good mix up until the rice is fully coated</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1696842224867-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1696842224867-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1696842224867-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1696842224867-x1000.jpg",
