            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1696842224867-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the <strong>browned chicken</strong> on top and put the dish in the oven, covered, for an initial 25 min</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1696843889909-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1696843889909-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1696843889909-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1696843889909-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1696843889909-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has had 25 min, top the dish with the <strong>pak choi quarters</strong></p><p>Return the dish to the oven, covered, for a further 5 min or until the veg is tender and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>one-pot Hainanese-style chicken & rice with pak choi</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1696843894030-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1696843894030-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1696843894030-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1696843894030-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1696843894030-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>one-pot Hainanese-style chicken & rice with pak choi </strong>in the middle of the table</p><p>Garnish with a<strong> lime wedge</strong>, your <strong>crispy onions </strong>and <strong>sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
      "order": 8,
